<plot>For the past two months, Steve Nelson has only had one thing on his mind: 'Why did my wife leave me?' She won't answer his calls and seems to have disappeared from town. Steve is alone. He doesn't fit in at his job and has lost all interest in being there. One morning, after discovering that their dog has died, Steve decides that he will no longer wait for Julie to come home. He will go out and find her himself.</plot><url>http://localhost:8983/solr/movie.html?151106</url></doc>
